decks.notes: The main concept of this deck is to quickly ramp up mana through devotion to green cards and efficient mana dorks, allowing for explosive plays with cards like Storm the Festival and Lair of the Hydra. The deck aims to overwhelm the opponent with powerful green creatures like Old-Growth Troll and Cavalier of Thorns, supported by Kiora, Behemoth Beckoner's card draw and ramp abilities. The inclusion of Boseiju, Who Endures helps protect key spells from countermagic, ensuring the deck can execute its game plan smoothly and efficiently.
